Hypo Alpe Preps Sale of Croatian Industry Stakes: WiBlatt Link

-- B y   B o r i s   G r o e n d a h l
-- 
2011-02-28T06:29:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-28/hypo-alpe-preps-sale-of-croatian-industry-stakes-wiblatt-link.html
Hypo Alpe-Adria-Bank International
AG, the lender nationalized by the Austrian state, is preparing
to sell its stakes in two Croatian industrial companies,
Austrian daily newspaper WirtschaftsBlatt reported.  Hypo Alpe may offer from April its stakes in packaging
maker Aluflexpack and aluminum maker TLM-TVP, WirtschaftsBlatt
said, citing informed sources. It got both stakes as a
collateral for loans that were not paid, the paper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
